      <title>英伟达股价剧烈波动，人工智能反弹势头受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/nvidia-s-wild-stock-swings-put-ai-rally-stamina-in-spotlight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 股价大幅波动再次引发了人们对这家芯片制造商股价能否持续上涨的争论。尽管该公司股价的估值和竞争威胁是主要担忧，但有一个变量至关重要：需求的持久性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/nvidia-s-wild-stock-swings-put-ai-rally-stamina-in-spotlight</guid>
